## What ?
epmail - smtp/pop3 mail server written in erlang.

## Install/run
    make
    cd ebin
    erl
    popd_listener:start_link().
    
First of all after server running create some users:
    maildir:adduser("localhost", "admin", "qwerty").
 
Then you can connect by telnet:

[shk@myhost ~]$ telnet localhost 110
Trying 127.0.0.1...
Connected to localhost.
Escape character is '^]'.
+OK POP3 server ready 
use shk
-ERR
user shk
+OK
pass qwerty
+OK
list 1
+OK 1 3507
.
noop
+OK

